thread.title: C Chaney
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by C Chaney

author: C Chaney
title: C Chaney
text:
I have made two business purchases from them in the last 30 days. I've found that their prices are well below that of the big retailers and they sell a high quality product. Their website is easy to use for custom designed products. They have a quick turn around time from the time order is placed, shipped, and delivered.
I am very satisfied with Rubber Stamp Champ and will definitely recommend them to my colleagues, friends, and family.
